name: The Storefront
description:
Inspired by Nahiko.

The-Storeftront.club played an important part for many musicians from indonesia. I released my debut album exclusively there on my birthday in June 2020. The rewards I got from betting on the platform is not only the money from album sales, but this overwhelming sense of revelation that people are still willing to spend their time & money to get access to things that most people think should be easily accessible, if they trust you enough. 

This is my way to celebrate the moment I became free. 

Since NFT also played a huge part in this realization, this is my way to bridge the so-called web 2 & 3. 

90% of the selling of this art will be contributed to everybody at The Storefront.
